params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.entity_type
params.description: Required. The resource name of the entities' type. Value format: projects/{project}/locations/{location}/featurestores/{featurestore}/entityTypes/{entityType}. For example, for a machine learning model predicting user clicks on a website, an EntityType ID could be user.

params.name: data.entity_ids
params.description: Required. IDs of entities to read Feature values of. The maximum number of IDs is 100. For example, for a machine learning model predicting user clicks on a website, an entity ID could be user_123.

params.name: data.feature_selector
params.description: Required. Selector choosing Features of the target EntityType. Feature IDs will be deduplicated.
